snippet.textDisplay:
Novak I love you with all my heart and soul and in awe of you for the compassion, kindness, generosity and spiritual value you bring to the world as well as for your achievements AND bringing us the greatest moments in tennis history....I do respect your views on the vaccination issue and do believe that each human being has a right to choose what happens to their body...sometimes, however, as weird/unjust/unfair the "rules" are, we all are coerced to align with these to get by, even when we are not totally convinced of its legitimacy...taxes/rates/laws/governments decisions, etc etc...I have taken the vaccination for many other reasons which were contrary to my personal view...was just being practical. 

Are you not going to play in any tournaments/slams if these rules are applied again as they have been in Aussie.....Still your choice to make and what a decision that would be if you choose to stick to the anti-vaccination stance again across these other tournaments....Yes, you will go down in history as a martyr in this regard but at what cost ...and then they will remain victorious in inhibiting your career ambitions and your tennis legacy (even tho they will never stifle/negate your humanitarian legacy and your honour)..

I pray for you and for your clarity/wisdom in these forthcoming decisions and will always love you irrespective of your choice....you will always be for me, the greatest tennis player and humanitarian I have known....God bless...sending you spiritual energy and strength always.😍😍😍

P.S I am not sure how reflective this tournament this will be WITHOUT the world no.1 competing...
